  "text": "We choose the initial conditions for the circularly polarized problem. Given the values of F and B, the energy of the system is chosen according to Ref. [CITATION_1] in the maximum configuration. At this energy, there is a stationary point of the flow and interesting dynamics happens in this case (see Ref. [CITATION_2] for more details). We notice that the stationary points belong to the surfaceP ρ = 0. The maximum configuration is obtained forṽ = 0, i.e. for",
